OL,3,CPub owner awarded Derby's Freedom of
OL,4,Cthe City after years of fundraising
OL,6,FA pub landlord who has raised more
OL,7,Fthan #120,000 for charity, has been
OL,8,Fawarded the Freedom of Derby.
OL,10,FSteve Kirk, who runs The Neptune pub
OL,11,Fon Osmaston Road, first began
OL,12,Fcollecting money for the Royal British
OL,13,FLegion more than 15 years ago.
OL,15,FHe's now been given the city's highest
OL,16,Fcivic honour in recognition of his
OL,17,F"exceptional" fundraising efforts.
