OL,3,CPub owner awarded Derby's Freedom of
OL,4,Cthe City after years of fundraising
OL,6,FSteve has also raised money for other
OL,7,Fcharities by doing a sponsored row,
OL,8,Fwalks, auctions and raffles, and even
OL,9,Fonce rowed 15 miles between Shardlow
OL,10,Fand Willington in Derbyshire.
OL,12,F"So proud and humbled, I love Derby"
OL,14,FAt today's ceremony, Steve said:
OL,16,F"So proud, humbled, chuffed for the
OL,17,Fpub and people of Derby.
OL,19,F"I love Derby. Derby's my home town
OL,20,F.... to get that it's just incredible".
