OL,6,FThe Royal British Legion alone
OL,7,Festimate that Steve has collected more
OL,8,Fmoney for their Poppy Appeal than any
OL,9,Fother pub in the UK.
OL,11,FThe man who nominated Steve for the
OL,12,Faward says he's much more than just a
OL,13,Ffund-raiser, saying:
OL,15,F"Steve I know for a fact, was the
OL,16,Ffirst person to volunteer at a
OL,17,Fvaccination centre when Covid 19 was
OL,18,Fhere, that's Steve".
