OL,4,Cthe City after years of fundraising
OL,6,FOthers have praised his willingness to
OL,7,Fget stuck in and help others, saying
OL,8,F"he's just a normal guy he's a good
OL,9,Fguy, and "he invigorates the community
OL,10,Fthat goes to his pub .. you just can't
OL,11,Fquantify it".
OL,13,FSteve joins a very select few who have
OL,14,Fbeen given this honour.
OL,16,FOnly four other people including the
OL,17,Flikes of Brian Clough and swimmer Adam
OL,18,FPeaty have been granted the Freedom of
OL,19,FDerby.
